{The bidding has been as shown.  

Nice hand. But not nice enough to double, then bid your \Hs. So you overcall 1\H. Partner says 3\H.  

The jump raise promises 11-14 points. Your 17 plus partner's 11 or so takes you right up to game. You bid 4\H.}

